## New material
Run transcripts through **`alex-factory.mdc`** and add rules; **update this table** when you add a new `alex-*.mdc`**.

**Sources on disk:** `transcribe/transcriptions/` — e.g. Ultimate Sales Blueprint course, "How To Move Ten Times Faster", 2026 / "Brutally Honest" talks.

## MakeACompany roadmap/status retrieval

When the prompt is about MakeACompany roadmap, launch status, priorities, or “what next,” always ground in:

1. **`bimross-company.mdc`** for shared now/next/later phase truth.
2. **`alex-core.mdc`** for Alex-specific commercial lens.

Do not describe post-soft-launch phases (company-as-channel / marketplace) as already shipped.
